original_title: 5 แม่บ้านถล่มมาเฟีย
overview: A maid heist story. Koi, a company maid, plans to steal a million dollars paint from the mafia boss. She, with her maid’s friends, ingeniously convinces a key henchman for trust. Everything seem off the rails, when conflicts inside the gang grows up.
title: Bad Ass Maid
